      <title>印度燃料零售商将在大选前下调柴油和汽油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/india-fuel-retailers-to-cut-diesel-gasoline-rate-ahead-of-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度国营燃料零售商将从周五开始下调柴油和汽油价格，这是近两年来的首次利率调整，距离全国选举仅几周时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/india-fuel-retailers-to-cut-diesel-gasoline-rate-ahead-of-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 16:54:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
